00:40:27,880 --> 00:40:29,000
Oh, don't say it like that.

1179
00:40:29,110 --> 00:40:30,760
You're running big business now.

1180
00:40:30,880 --> 00:40:32,630
How could I possibly help you?

1181
00:40:34,320 --> 00:40:35,230
I just feel a little

1182
00:40:37,150 --> 00:40:38,630
reluctant to leave it here.

1183
00:40:40,800 --> 00:40:41,840
Do you have to go?

1184
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:47,000
Yes.

1185
00:40:48,670 --> 00:40:50,000
Then I'll send it to you by express.

1186
00:40:51,000 --> 00:40:51,840
I asked around.

1187
00:40:52,150 --> 00:40:53,480
Shipping is too expensive.

1188
00:40:53,920 --> 00:40:54,630
And besides,

1189
00:40:55,150 --> 00:40:56,590
you know Shenxian Peak.

1190
00:40:56,840 --> 00:40:58,550
There's nowhere to ride a bike.

1191
00:41:12,630 --> 00:41:13,150
Wanzhi,

1192
00:41:13,800 --> 00:41:15,110
do you want to ride another lap?

1193
00:41:16,280 --> 00:41:16,760
Alright.

1194
00:41:17,320 --> 00:41:17,800
Let's go.

1195
00:41:24,110 --> 00:41:24,760
Wanzhi,

1196
00:41:25,480 --> 00:41:26,480
do you want

1197
00:41:26,480 --> 00:41:27,440
to hear me sing?

1198
00:41:34,510 --> 00:41:35,110
Wanzhi,

1199
00:41:35,710 --> 00:41:38,000
let me sing a song for you.

1200
00:41:39,230 --> 00:41:40,320
You can sing?

1201
00:41:41,280 --> 00:41:42,630
Shenxian Peak's song.

1202
00:41:43,070 --> 00:41:43,880
Want to hear it?

1203
00:41:44,110 --> 00:41:44,480
Okay!

1204
00:41:44,630 --> 00:41:45,070
Alright!

1205
00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:48,480
Shenxian Peak, oh, Shenxian Peak,

1206
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:52,630
the place where immortals live.

1207
00:41:56,150 --> 00:41:56,920
How is it?

1208
00:41:57,400 --> 00:41:58,630
Very nice! Encore!

1209
00:42:07,800 --> 00:42:08,320
Okay.

1210
00:42:09,030 --> 00:42:09,960
Will this do?

1211
00:42:10,280 --> 00:42:11,670
Don't worry about it.

1212
00:42:11,880 --> 00:42:13,230
Express delivery in Shenzhen

1213
00:42:13,440 --> 00:42:14,510
is very convenient now.

1214
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:15,760
There's a service point

1215
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:16,760
outside the parking lot.

1216
00:42:16,960 --> 00:42:17,800
Three days tops.

1217
00:42:18,110 --> 00:42:19,000
And Mr. He

1218
00:42:19,230 --> 00:42:20,030
will receive it

1219
00:42:20,030 --> 00:42:20,960
at Shenxian Peak.

1220
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:21,880
Okay.

1221
00:42:22,400 --> 00:42:23,190
Thanks, Jia.

1222
00:42:23,280 --> 00:42:24,280
You're welcome. I'll head off.

1223
00:42:28,920 --> 00:42:29,710
Want some garlic?

1224
00:42:31,230 --> 00:42:33,110
Have some! It tastes nice!

1225
00:42:33,190 --> 00:42:33,630
No.

1226
00:42:37,230 --> 00:42:38,480
I've been so busy that I haven't

1227
00:42:38,480 --> 00:42:39,670
had a chance to see Mr. He off.

1228
00:42:39,760 --> 00:42:40,480
It's fine.

1229
00:42:41,360 --> 00:42:41,960
He said

1230
00:42:42,280 --> 00:42:43,630
he'll book a flight for you two

1231
00:42:43,960 --> 00:42:44,630
to go there

1232
00:42:44,880 --> 00:42:45,670
for his 80th birthday.

1233
00:42:45,880 --> 00:42:47,070
Oh my! That sounds good.

1234
00:42:49,320 --> 00:42:50,440
Why isn't Qian here for the meal?
